data.description: Looking for a cozy and private home in a great location? Look no further than this one-story 3/2 with a small lot that offers plenty of privacy. This home features some new laminate flooring, a two-car garage, an island kitchen, and a large master bedroom with a walk-in closet. You'll love the convenience of walking to the nearby elementary school and the security of living in a controlled access neighborhood with a park and playground. Don't miss this opportunity to own this charming home!
